<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; text-align: center; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
  
  <h1 style="color: #333;">OCR 메뉴판 번역기 웹앱</h1>
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1.1em;">
    한국어 메뉴판 이미지를 업로드하면 자동으로 텍스트를 추출하고 번역해 드립니다.
  </p>

  <hr style="margin: 20px 0;">

  <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <h2 style="color: #e00;">⚙️ 사용 기술 스택</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 30px;">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <%= image_tag "ruby-logo.png", alt: "Ruby Logo", style: "height: 60px;" %> 
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0;">**Ruby 3.3.0**</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <%= image_tag "rails-logo.png", alt: "Rails Logo", style: "height: 60px;" %> 
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0;">**Rails 7.1.x**</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 15px;">
      <li>**OCR Engine:** Tesseract OCR (w/ 한국어 팩)</li>
      <li>**Translation API:** DeepL API Free Tier</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <hr style="margin: 20px 0;">

  <%= form_with model: @menu_entry, url: menu_entries_path, local: true, html: { style: "display: inline-block; padding: 20px; border: 2px dashed #e00; border-radius: 5px;" } do |form| %>
    <div class="field" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <%= form.label :image, "메뉴판 이미지 선택", style: "font-size: 1.2em; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;" %><br>
      <%= form.file_field :image, required: true, style: "padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;" %>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <%= form.submit "번역 시작하기", style: "background-color: #e00; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1em;" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

</div>